OL,3,CParking company pays out over #7,000
OL,4,Cafter claims it was 'preying on
OL,5,Cvulnerable'
OL,7,FA parking company has paid out
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds - and overhauled
OL,9,Fits policy - after patients at a West
OL,10,FYorkshire health centre claimed it was
OL,11,F'preying on vulnerable people'.
OL,13,FThe company UK Car Parking Management
OL,14,Fwas brought in to 'prevent people who
OL,15,Fwere not patients abusing the system'.
OL,17,FPatients were then required to enter
OL,18,Ftheir registration when they attended
OL,19,Fthe surgery.
