OL,3,CParking company pays out over #7,000
OL,4,Cafter claims it was 'preying on
OL,5,Cvulnerable'
OL,7,FBut some patients had been fined up to
OL,8,F#470 after attending multiple
OL,9,Fappointments - and either not
OL,10,Frealising, forgetting, or inputting
OL,11,Ftheir car registration incorrectly.
OL,12,FTheir fines increased on appeal - and
OL,13,Fproof of appointment was not accepted.
OL,15,FNow though, patients who did prove
OL,16,Fthey had an appointment - have been
OL,17,Frefunded.
