OL,3,CParking company pays out over #7,000
OL,4,Cafter claims it was 'preying on
OL,5,Cvulnerable'
OL,7,FMirfield councillor Vivien Lees-
OL,8,FHamilton said it showed the 'power of
OL,9,Fthe people'. She added: ''I've loved
OL,10,Fevery minute of it. To see that they
OL,11,Fcan appeal, they did get their money
OL,12,Fback - and things have been set right.
OL,13,FIt's what I do as a councillor - stand
OL,14,Fup for people who can't stand up for
OL,15,Fthemselves. We must have got more than
OL,16,F#7,000 for 50 people.
OL,18,F''It's been fantastic coverage. Local
OL,19,Fmedia is brilliant for combating local
OL,20,Fissues. It raises the profile - and it
OL,21,Fgot a brilliant result.
