OL,3,CParking company pays out over #7,000
OL,4,Cafter claims it was 'preying on
OL,5,Cvulnerable'
OL,7,F''One single mum who was sent into her
OL,8,Foverdraft after the fine - the #270
OL,9,Fappeared back in her account after the
OL,10,Fpiece went out.''
OL,12,FAndy Breare, whose 83-year-old father
OL,13,Fwas fined - and now refunded - after a
OL,14,F12 minute appointment, said: ''My dad
OL,15,Fhad been very stressed about it and
OL,16,Fdidn't understand. Thanks to proper
OL,17,Flocal journalism this appalling
OL,18,Fsituation was exposed. We are so
OL,19,Fhappy.''
